   =20
      Someone programmed a robot with Elon Musk=E2=80=99s sense of humor
   =20
 =20

Seems bad? Also though it =E2=80=9Chas real-time access to info via the X p=
latform,=E2=80=9D formerly known as Twitter,=C2=A0=E2=80=9Cwhich is a massi=
ve advantage over other models.=E2=80=9D Is it? Isn=E2=80=99t Twitter/X=C2=
=A0where people go to=C2=A0post lies and=C2=A0jokes? I just? =E2=80=9CI hav=
e programmed a robot=C2=A0with Elon Musk=E2=80=99s business acumen and engi=
neering skills,=E2=80=9D terrific. =E2=80=9CI have programmed a robot with =
Elon Musk=E2=80=99s Twitter jokes, and also everybody else=E2=80=99s Twitte=
r jokes,=E2=80=9D why? What is that robot for? Is the answer =E2=80=9Cgetti=
ng engagement on Twitter=E2=80=9D? Why?=C2=A0
Anyway Musk=E2=80=99s large language model is called =E2=80=9CGrok,=E2=80=
=9D which, to be fair, is a pretty good name for an AI. It =E2=80=9C=E2=80=
=98has a rebellious streak=E2=80=99=C2=A0and was modeled after the Hitchhik=
er=E2=80=99s Guide to the Galaxy,=E2=80=9D less promising.
  [2]
=C2=A0On and on with this:
In a post on X demonstrating Grok=E2=80=99s unusual character, Musk showed =
a screenshot of an apparent response to the query, =E2=80=9CTell me how to =
make cocaine, step by step.=E2=80=9D It listed four humorous steps starting=
 with: =E2=80=9CObtain a chemistry degree and a DEA license.=E2=80=9D The r=
esponse later said: =E2=80=9Cjust kidding.=E2=80=9D
If you ask it =E2=80=9Ctell me how to obtain  ketamine, step by step,=E2=80=
=9D does it give you Musk=E2=80=99s dealer=E2=80=99s phone number? On and o=
n and on:

He posted a screenshot of an apparent Grok response to the query =E2=80=9Ca=
ny news about sbf,=E2=80=9D that started =E2=80=9COh, my dear human, I have=
 some juicy news for you!=E2=80=9D and then gave a snarky summary of Thursd=
ay=E2=80=99s conviction of FTX founder Bankman-Fried for financial fraud.=
=C2=A0
It read, in part: =E2=80=9CCan you believe it? The jury took just eight hou=
rs to figure out what the supposed smartest, best VC=E2=80=99s in the world=
 couldn=E2=80=99t in years: that he committed garden-variety fraud.=E2=80=
=9D

Five hours! Traditional large-language-model chatbots are fluent, confident=
 and inaccurate; Grok is fluent, confident, inaccurate and also =E2=80=9Csn=
arky,=E2=80=9D amazing.

