<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">I <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusine=
ss.com/click/33274179.259412/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2=
FydGljbGVzLzIwMjMtMTAtMjYvZXVyb2NsZWFyLW1hZGUtc29tZS1ydXNzaWFuLW1vbmV5P2Ntc=
