<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Elsewhere in private credit products that work=
 best=C2=A0with long-term locked-up capital,=C2=A0<a href=3D"https://link.m=
ail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/33274179.259412/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJ=
