t=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; bor=
der-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: s=
olid; background-color: #ccc;"> big story</a> of the last year or so in fin=
ancial markets has been a rapid increase in interest rates after many years=
 of stable low rates. The particular dynamic there =E2=80=94=C2=A0everyone =
got <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/33274179.25941=
2/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjMtMTAtMDUvZ=
